    "Variable best fitness order-Our proposed model for predicting the success probability of 6G-SQC projects yields two primary advantages.",
    "First, it offers an optimal cost distribution across various variables to maximize project success probability.",
    "Second, it sheds light on the relative importance of these variables.",
    "Table 3 outlines the variable costs needed to achieve close to 100% project success.",
    "This indicates that certain variables might be less crucial, as high success rates can be sustained even at lower cost values."
